## Block 1: `viz-office-map`

**Concept:** Animated 3D globe showing company office locations with live headcount,
status (open/closed/remote-day), and a live "pulse" animation on active offices.
Clicking a pin opens a sidebar with office details, local time, and a sparkline of
recent activity. Looks incredible on an About Us or Careers page.

**Data format (JSON from URL):**
```json
[{"id":"sf","label":"San Francisco","lat":37.77,"lon":-122.41,"headcount":420,
  "status":"open","timezone":"America/Los_Angeles","activity":[12,18,34,41,38,29]}]
```
Inline fallback: 8 hard-coded Adobe office locations with realistic data.

**Rendering:**
- Three.js sphere with subtle day/night shader based on current UTC time
  (sunlit hemisphere glows, dark side dims)
- Office pins: glowing animated THREE.PointLight halos, color by status
  (green=open, amber=hybrid, grey=closed)
- Click pin → slide-in panel with local clock (live), headcount badge, activity sparkline
- Globe auto-tilts to show most offices; drag/zoom enabled; slow auto-rotation pauses on hover

**Fields:** `dataUrl` (text), `inlineData` (text-area), `height` (text), `theme` (select: dark/light)

